    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "It seems to come from the fact that `connectRange` always set the `$$type` to `ais.range`.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/ada37ae054275d46cc2edaee0081562b6c35cbc8/src/connectors/range/connectRange.js#L74-L75\r\n\r\nand `checkIndexUiState` assumes that a `range` can only have `ais.rangeInput` or `ais.rangeSlider` NOT `ais.range`\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/ada37ae054275d46cc2edaee0081562b6c35cbc8/src/lib/utils/checkIndexUiState.ts#L57-L60\r\n",
